{"tid":1268120,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非，630係機會啦！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-30T08:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T09:08:12.000Z","uid":264459,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aa31c2fe31e036aefc85026a7e62446d698c0a62","tid":1268120,"uid":264459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T08:07:38.000Z","msg":"烈士為我哋以死明志  勇武為我哋受傷<br />\n講明兄弟爬山 <br />\n和理非都一樣有其用武之處<br />\n<br />\n除左日頭行動中湊人數夾物資 <br />\n我哋更加要係每個看似危險既晚上 同勇武巴絲互相守護<br />\n實踐人越多越安全既理念<br />\n<br />\n630煲底需要我哋幫手做後援 守住物資<br />\n令朝早升旗禮可以順利行動<br />\n<br />\n630夜晚9點，煲底見！！！！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n朝早打機攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://docdro.id/bRhD3cC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocdro.id%2FbRhD3cC&d=ZcVshzlQZ77dxUPC5JM1BAp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=95b5cac0\" target=\"_blank\">https://docdro.id/bRhD3cC</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qytz9qg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqytz9qg.png&h=f0f3ffa3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vFbmPqh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvFbmPqh.jpg&h=5890c125&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOuPdRX.jpg\" d